TitleEnglish: Inazuma Eleven the Movie: The New Heroes' Prologue
SummaryEnglish: Gekijouban Inazuma Eleven: Aratanaru Eiyu-tachi no Josho ("Inazuma Eleven the Movie: Prologue of The New Heroes") tells a prologue to the story of Inazuma Eleven: Victory Road , the latest installment in the game series.
